<template>      
    <v-row class='filterdiv' align="center">
      <v-col class="d-flex form-item" cols="12" sm="5" md='3'>
        <v-select
          :items="items"
          label="Şöbələr"
          outlined
        ></v-select>
      </v-col>
       <v-col class="d-flex form-item" cols="12" sm="5" md='3'>
        <v-select
          :items="items"
          label="Müqavilənin tipi"
          outlined
        ></v-select>
      </v-col>
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
      <v-col class="buttons-bar" cols="12" sm="2" md='1'>
          <v-btn  icon router to="/crnewagreement" >
        <v-icon>create_new_folder</v-icon>
      </v-btn>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name:"Filterbar",
       data: () => ({
      items: ['Hamisi', 'Bar', 'Fizz', 'Buzz'],
    }),
}
</script>

<style>
     .filterdiv{
          display: flex; 
           margin: 0px!important;
          box-shadow: 0 0 13px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
           background-color: #ffffff;
           margin: 10px!important;
     }
     .v-input{
         font-size: 14px!important;
     }
      .v-input__append-inner{
              margin-top: 4px!important;
      }
      .v-select__selections{
         padding: 0px!important;

      }
      .v-input__slot{
          min-width: unset!important;
             margin-bottom: 0px!important;
              min-height: unset!important;
      }
      .v-text-field.v-text-field--enclosed .v-text-field__details
       {
      margin-bottom: 0px!important;  
}

 .v-text-field--outlined .v-label {
    top: 6px!important;
}
 .filterdiv .v-label.v-label--active.theme--light.primary--text {
    top:18px!important
}  

 .filterdiv .v-label.v-label--active.theme--light {
    top:18px!important
} 

.form-item{
    padding-bottom: 0px!important;
}

.buttons-bar{ 
  text-align: right!important;
}

.buttons-bar a{ 
  color: #2294F2!important;
}
</style>
